#: ../../source/configure/calls-deployment.md:99
msgid ""
"Calls performance primarily depends on two resources: CPU and bandwidth "
"(both network latency and overall throughput). The final consumption "
"exhibits quadratic growth with the number of clients transmitting and "
"receiving media."
